sentences: Alih Jey (born May 5, 1984) is a Dominican rock music singer and songwriter.
Alih Jey released her debut album, Alih Jey, in 2001.
Her second album Gotas De Piel was released to great critical acclaim in 2005.
In 2005, Alih Jey toured alongside Mexican star Paulina Rubio during Rubio's Pau-Latina tour across the United States.
In 2006, she severed ties with record label Universal Music Latino and proceeded to work on a new independent record, Necia, released the following year.
